## Personal Use Guidelines

**You MAY (for personal, non-commercial use):**
- Use this code as a template for your own portfolio
- Modify and customize the design and functionality
- Learn from the implementation patterns
- Reference the prompt engineering methodologies
- Share with others (with attribution)

**You MUST:**
- Provide attribution as specified above
- Replace all personal information (name, photo, bio, contact info)
- Replace prompt examples with your own content if using as portfolio
- Not imply endorsement by Basiliso Rosario

**You MAY NOT (without written permission):**
- Use for commercial purposes (selling, monetizing, business use)
- Use in paid training materials or courses
- Include in products or services sold to others
- Remove or obscure attribution notices
- Claim the work as entirely your own creation

